title: Frank Zappa - The Lost Episodes 1996 (feat. Captain Beefheart)
description:
This is a superb collection of previously unreleased Frank Zappa gems, mostly from the earlier end of his career, beginning as early as 1958, but in the main confined to the 1960s and early '70s.

Captain Beefheart is featured on five of the tracks.

Zappa knew he was heading for his last encore and worked on this album of out-takes, studio tomfoolery and unreleased tracks in the years before he died in 1993.



Frank Zappa

The Lost Episodes

1996
